window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Annual Freshman Rumble is about to begin, and the stakes are high.</b></p> <p>My team and I have worked hard to earn the honor of representing Krysfelt Academy for Girls, but not everyone is happy to see us rise to the top. Old rivalries are resurfacing, and some competitors are willing to take things too far.</p> <p>We’ll need to draw on everything we’ve ever learned, strengthen our bonds, and face rivals both new and old. This will be the ultimate test for our team.</p>"; 
